\begin_layout Abstract

\series bold
How to Configure your LaTeX Distribution with kuthesis.cls
\end_layout

\begin_layout Abstract
I wish we had packaged 
\family typewriter
kuthesis.cls
\family default
 into an official LaTeX distribution package so that it could be easily
 installed by your distribution.
 We did not do that, however, and so it is up to you to place a copy of
 
\family typewriter
kuthesis.cls
\family default
 in the right spot
\family typewriter
.

\family default
 This is not truly necessary.
 Programs like pdflatex will find 
\family typewriter
kuthesis.cls
\family default
 if you have it in the same directory as the document.
 I believe, with 97.5% confidence, it will find 
\family typewriter
kuthesis.cls
\family default
 if you keep it in the same directory as your document.
 If you want to use kuthesis.cls for several documents, it is necessary to
 install 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\family typewriter
kuthesis.cls
\family default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 into your \SpecialChar LaTeX
 file structure.
 That is generally an easy process, but it is different on every type of
 computer.
 The CRMDA staff has recently prepared a guide for this, entitled 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

How Users can Install \SpecialChar LaTeX
 packages without Help from System Administrators
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Flex URL
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

https://crmda.ku.edu/guide-32-latex_config
\end_layout

\end_inset

).
 The gist of this is as follows:
\begin_inset Separator latexpar
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Copy 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\family typewriter
kuthesis.cls
\family default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 into a directory in your \SpecialChar LaTeX
 distribution.
 Usually (almost always), you will find a directory component that ends
 in 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

tex/latex
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and you can put kuthesis.cls in there.
 The only puzzle is finding the right place, and that's why you should review
 our guide.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Run 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

texhash
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 or to make the \SpecialChar LaTeX
 distribution take notice of your new file.
 On Mac and Linux systems, open a terminal and run 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\family typewriter
sudo texhash
\family default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 to get this done as the administrator.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Abstract

\series bold
How to Get Started on this with \SpecialChar LyX

\end_layout

\begin_layout Abstract
This document with \SpecialChar LyX
! It will work.
 LyX is a pleasant-to-use editor, it can protect you from some of the details
 that ordinary \SpecialChar LaTeX
 will present.
 \SpecialChar LyX
 is free to use on all major computing platforms, including Linux, Macintosh,
 and Windows.
 \SpecialChar LyX
 can be downloaded at 
\begin_inset Flex URL
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://www.lyx.org
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 To make this work, LaTeX programs are also needed.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Mac users: install the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

MacTeX
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 package (
\begin_inset Flex URL
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

https://www.tug.org/mactex
\end_layout

\end_inset

).
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Linux users: install your distribution's version of TeXLive or install the
 TeXLive files from the TeXLive website (
\begin_inset Flex URL
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

https://www.tug.org/texlive
\end_layout

\end_inset

) .
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Windows Users: The LyX website offers 2 choices, a LyX-only package and
 an 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

installer bundle
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 that includes LyX along with a small subset of the MikTeX LaTeX distribution.
 This installs just a small subset of MikTeX and pieces can be separately
 downloaded when needed.
 In Fall, 2016, we had some difficulties during a LaTeX workshop because
 the MikTeX package server was unavailable.
 As a result, we have been migrating away from MikTeX (and the LyX installer
 bundle) to use TeXLive for Windows (
\begin_inset Flex URL
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

https://www.tug.org/texlive
\end_layout

\end_inset

).
 That's a big 2GB package like MacTeX, after that we install the LyX program.
 If you choose the MikTeX setup instead, it will usually be fine, but users
 often complain that LyX seems to 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

freeze
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 when it downloads new MikTeX components.
\end_layout

